	dprr:hasNoteText "Monetalis. In MRR 2.455, and Index, 634, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.346-351, no. 342, 90 B.C. He was probably the adoptive father of the consul of 43 (see below, no. 16). See Wiseman, CQ 14, 1964, 131; NM 274, no. 490; Rowland, TAPhA 97, 1966, 409-410.\n" ;
